{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21321.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"sepiaFrame"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","nameNarration":"莉薇娅","narration":"在被蒙上眼罩、昏迷过去之后@我睁开眼睛时@身处的已经不再是自己的故乡了","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-1"},{"narration":"看风景只能明白这里被大自然包围@并不知道具体在哪里@说不定还是在日本","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-2"},{"narration":"但是，从窗户飘入的空气的香味@让我感到自己好像到了一个不同的国度","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-3"},{"narration":"我很快就开始在剧团里练习魔术和幻术@据说和我的祖先来自同一个国家的孩子@成为了我的搭档","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-4"},{"narration":"而且，通过练习@我也和其他国家的人搞好了关系","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-5"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":2,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-6"},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104102,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"诶，这个幻术里@躯干没切断就不行吧？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":104102,"motion":400,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-7"}],"nameLeft":"莉薇娅","textLeft":"不对，是镜子角度的问题@再从基础开始挑战一次吧"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":800300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-8"}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"嗯，是啊","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104102},{"effect":"fadeout","id":800300}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_21321.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":800400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103201/vo_full_103201-15-9"}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"嘿，1、2、3、4"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":800400,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","i